payload.content:
Thought: 通过文件搜索和读取，已定位到 flybird_game/index.html 文件，该文件是 FlyBird 游戏的主入口页面。当前界面使用了 styles-cartoon.css 样式文件，但未找到该文件，因此需要创建一个符合卡通风格的样式文件来优化 UI 界面。接下来将创建一个新的 CSS 样式文件以实现更卡通、美观的视觉效果。

Action: file_write[{"path": "flybird_game/styles-cartoon.css", "content": "/* 卡通风格的 UI 样式 */
body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffebcc, #b3d9ff);
    font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}

#game-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 400px;
    height: 600px;
    border: 8px solid #ff69b4;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    overflow: hidden;
}

#game-canvas {
    background: url('https://i.imgur.com/5NjKvXq.png') no-repeat center center;
    background-size: cover;
}

#ui {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border: 3px solid #ff69b4;
}

#start-btn, #pause-btn {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    background: #ff69b4;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

#start-btn:hover, #pause-btn:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    background: #ff1493;
}

#score, #history {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #333;
    background: #fffaf0;
    padding: 8px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 2px solid #ffd700;
    text-align: center;
}

#score {
    color: #ff4500;
}

#history {
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: #006400;
}

/* 动画效果 */
@keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}

#start-btn, #pause-btn {
    animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
}", "overwrite": true]}

